    <div class="row span10">
        <h1>Options</h1>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <code>ignoreColumns</code>
                <ul>
                    <li>Column indexes to not make filterable</li>
                    <li>
                        Type: <code>Array</code>
                    </li>
                    <li>Default: <code>[]</code></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <code>onlyColumns</code>
                <ul>
                    <li>Column indexes to make filterable, all other columns are left non-filterable.</li>
                    <li>This takes presidence over <code>ignoreColumns</code> when both are provided.</li>
                    <li>
                        Type: <code>Array</code>
                    </li>
                    <li>Default: <code>null</code> - all columns</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <code>ignoreCase</code>
                <ul>
                    <li>If case should be ignored</li>
                    <li>Type: <code>Boolean</code></li>
                    <li>Default: <code>true</code></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <code>isMatch</code>
                <ul>
                    <li>Define your own function to determine if a cell matches the user's query or not.</li>
                    <li>Type: <code>function($cell, query)</code></li>
                    <li>Default: <code>null</code></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <code>editableOptions</code>
                <ul>
                    <li>Any custom options for X-editable.</li>
                    <li>Type: <code>Object</code></li>
                    <li>Default: <code>{}</code></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <code>editableSelector</code>
                <ul>
                    <li>Selector to use on each heading to define the x-editable object. If not supplied, the entire heading is used.</li>
                    <li>Type: <code>String</code></li>
                    <li>Default: <code>null</code></li>
                    <li>Example: <code>editableSelector: 'i[class="icon-filter"]'</code> make only the filter icons clickable vs. the entire heading.</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <code>beforeFilter</code>
                <ul>
                    <li>Function to call before filtering a column.</li>
                    <li>Type: <code>Function</code></li>
                    <li>Default: <code>null</code></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
                <code>afterFilter</code>
                <ul>
                    <li>Function to call after filtering a column.</li>
                    <li>Type: <code>Function</code></li>
                    <li>Default: <code>null</code></li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>